---
title: BBQ-Sauced Falafel Plates with Jalapeno Popper Creamed Corn and Broccoli
description: Who says BBQ plates have to be about meat? Crispy falafel dressed with sweet and smoky BBQ are paired with jalapeño popper-inspired corn and garlic broccoli.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/falafels-a-la-sauce-bbq-630c4cf3.jpg
